name: Caeliferatum M. - flattened
description:
Scenes from the Post-Anthropocene

Trampled on by a deer trying to evade a predator, probably a coyote
these things happened before
as they happen now
nothing has changed

--

Gouache and colored pencil on masa paper, scanned and edited digitally.

--

I'm interested in what survives after the age of man is over. What is the legacy we leave behind? Exploring the impacts on hereditary lines, ecologies, and forced evolution.
